        <h2 class="heading01">Security and other measures</h2>
        <p>
            Hair Decoded goes to great lengths to ensure that your information is safe and secure. However, we cannot offer guarantees that hackers or unauthorized personnel will not gain access to your personal information despite our best efforts in this regard. Be aware that in using our website and other related services, will mean that the information you provide passes through third-party platforms/ infrastructures not under our jurisdiction.
        </p>
        <p>
            Hair Decoded cannot protect, as well as this Privacy policy, information and data that you pass on to third party websites or other users of our services. It is important to state that you should keep personal or identifying information away from others. If you do feel an individual is trying to obtain your personal information under pretenses impersonating Hair Decoded and our services or other users, do not hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:info@hairdecoded.com">info@hairdecoded.com</a>.
        </p>
        <h2 class="heading01">No-Trail Policy</h2>
        <p>
            It is possible that you can set your device to automatically transmit a "Do Not Track" signal to websites and online service you visit, including Hair Decoded's web pages. However, note that no clear industry standard adequately defines a 'Do Not Track' in all ramifications. In the light of this development, Hair Decoded does not respond to 'Do Not Track' signals and related instructions from web browsers, similar to many other websites and online services platform.
        </p>

        <p>
            If at any point in the future, Hair decoded creates a program or protocol to respond to such web browser "Do Not Track" instructions, we will notify you of the details of that protocol in this Privacy Policy. To obtain more information on 'Do Not Track' visit <a href="https://www.aboutdnt.com/" target="_blank">https://www.aboutdnt.com</a>
        </p>

        <h2 class="heading01">Privacy Rights of Californians</h2>
        <p>
            Users of Hair Decoded website, who are resident or natives of California can enjoy special consideration. This consideration allows this set of users request and obtains from Hair Decoded once a year and at no cost, specific information about the personal data (if any) we made available to third-party agents, for direct marketing purposes in the preceding calendar year. Where applicable, this information would include a list of the categories of personal data that was shared and the names and addresses of all third parties with which we shared information in the immediately preceding calendar year.
        </p>
        <p>
