        </p>
        <h2 class="heading01">Alterations to the Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>
            Hair Decoded reserves the right to effect changes to her privacy policy, at any point in time, without recourse to users. In this regard, Hair Decoded enjoins users and visitors to frequently check this page for any alterations to the privacy policy. Should you continue to use Hair Decoded Services after any changes to this Privacy Policy, it shall constitute your tacit approval of such amendment (s).
        </p>

